<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Throughout the Oriental region from the Indian subcontinent through Southeast Asia, Indonesia to New Guinea and the Western Pacific islands; tropical Africa, Madagascar and the Seychelles. Recorded in the study region from Bangladesh, India (Andaman Is, Arunachal Pradesh*, Assam*, Meghalaya*, Nicobar Is, West Bengal), Laos, Myanmar, Taiwan, Thailand, Vietnam.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
